## Proposed Changes

### 1. Backend: Custom JWT & Auth Endpoints

We will implement the authentication logic in the `users` app.

#### [MODIFY] [settings.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/core/settings.py)
- Add `'rest_framework_simplejwt.token_blacklist'` to `INSTALLED_APPS`.
- Add custom authentication backends supporting email/username login.

#### [NEW] [serializers.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/users/serializers.py)
- **ProfileSerializer**: Serializes fields `bio`, `title`, `skills`, `is_approved`, `avatar`.
- **UserSerializer**: Serializes `id`, `username`, `email`, `role`, and nested `profile`.
- **RegisterSerializer**: Validates registration inputs, checks role permissions (allows registering only `STUDENT` or `MENTOR`), and creates user and profile in a transaction.
- **CustomTokenObtainPairSerializer**: Subclasses SimpleJWT's obtain serializer to inject user details (`id`, `username`, `email`, `role`, `is_approved`) in the login response body.
- **PasswordResetRequestSerializer**: Validates email request for password reset.
- **PasswordResetConfirmSerializer**: Validates reset token and updates the password.

#### [MODIFY] [views.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/users/views.py)
- **RegisterView**: API View utilizing `RegisterSerializer` and returning JWT tokens directly for auto-login.
- **CustomTokenObtainPairView**: Subclasses SimpleJWT view to use custom serializer.
- **ProfileView**: Retrieve (GET) and update (PUT/PATCH) for the authenticated user (`/api/auth/profile/`).
- **LogoutView**: API View that takes the refresh token, blacklists it, and clears any session details.
- **PasswordResetRequestView**: Generate a mock token, log the reset email link to console.
- **PasswordResetConfirmView**: Accept token and new password, updating user credentials.

#### [MODIFY] [urls.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/users/urls.py)
Map urls:
- `POST api/auth/register/` -> `RegisterView`
- `POST api/auth/login/` -> `CustomTokenObtainPairView`
- `POST api/auth/refresh/` -> `TokenRefreshView`
- `POST api/auth/logout/` -> `LogoutView`
- `GET/PUT/PATCH api/auth/profile/` -> `ProfileView`
- `POST api/auth/password-reset/` -> `PasswordResetRequestView`
- `POST api/auth/password-reset/confirm/` -> `PasswordResetConfirmView`

