- Run backend unit tests:
  - `python manage.py test users` to test Registration validation, Email/Username Login, Profile retrieval/updates, and password resets.
  - Test JWT token generation, expiration, and blacklisting.

### Manual Verification
- **Web App UI Walkthrough**:
  - Run the React Vite server and Django server.
  - Register a new Student. Verify redirect to Dashboard.
  - Register a new Mentor. Check that Mentor-specific fields (Title, Skills) are saved, and check that the Dashboard indicates "Awaiting Admin Approval".
  - Log out. Verify that the refresh token is blacklisted on the backend (cannot be reused to get a new access token).
  - Log in using either Username or Email.
  - Update user profile details and verify updates persist on refresh.
  - Check light/dark mode responsiveness.
